nodes.text: Princess Raiyah bint Hussein (born February 9, 1986) is the daughter of King Hussein, the former King of Jordan, and Queen Noor of Jordan. She  portrays Jaiyna Sibinth in an uncredited cameo in the 2019 film Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker, which was partially shot in the Wadi Rum desert in Raiyah's homeland.
